  <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-status bg-purple"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Traveling 🚌</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
        <p>
        <div class="text-muted">Sadly, this year we are not able to offer travel reimbursments. <b>However</b>, we are sending buses to Boston and New York.</div></p>
