        <br>
          <a href="https://mlh.io/seasons/na-2018/events" class="btn btn-secondary">Sign Up for Boston Bus</a>
          <br>
          <a href="https://mlh.io/seasons/na-2018/events" class="btn btn-secondary">Sign Up for New York Bus</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-status bg-blue"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Getting to the Hackathon 🚶‍</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
        <p><div class="text-muted">HackUMass happens at the Integrated Learning Center(ILC) at the University of Massachusetts Amherst.</div></p>
